{"title":"Django安装与配置","date":"2018-12-29T02:41:59.000Z","slug":"django","tags":["Django"],"categories":["Python"],"updated":"2019-01-08T12:20:04.158Z","content":"<p>1.在pycharm中创建Python项目  – hellodjango</p>\n<p>2.pip install django pymysql django-redis djangorestframework pillow    – 在Terminal的虚拟环境中安装依赖项</p>\n<p>pip check - 检查下载的依赖库之间是否冲突<br>pip freeze - 检查版本<br>python -m pip install -U 依赖库名    - 更新<br>pip install django==1.11 - 回到旧版本</p>\n<p>pip freeze &gt; requirements.txt - 把依赖库版本号重定向到一个文件<br>pip install -r requirements.txt - 按照文件安装依赖库</p>\n<p>3.django-admin startproject 项目名   - 创建一个django项目</p>\n<p>4.python manage.py runserver - 让项目运行起来 默认IP为127.0.0.1 默认端口为8000</p>\n<p>python namage.py runserver 端口    - 修改启动端口</p>\n<p>python manage.py runserver 0.0.0.0:80 - 修改IP和端口，端口设置为80访问时不用输入端口</p>\n<p>5.修改配置文件</p>\n<p>连接数据库MySQL</p>\n<p>在__init__.py中添加</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">import pymysql</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">pymysql.install_as_MySQLdb()</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>修改settings</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">DATABASES = &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &apos;default&apos;: &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &apos;ENGINE&apos;: &apos;django.db.backends.mysql&apos;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &apos;NAME&apos;: &apos;XX&apos;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &apos;HOST&apos;: &apos;XXXXXX&apos;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &apos;PORT&apos;: XXXX,</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &quot;USER&quot;: &apos;XX&apos;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &apos;PASSWORD&apos;: &apos;XXXXXX&apos;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &apos;TIME_ZONE&apos;: &apos;XXXX&apos;  # 设置时区 Asia/Chongqing</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">设置为中文</span><br><span class=\"line\">LANGUAGE_CODE = &apos;zh-hans&apos;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">TIME_ZONE = &apos;XXXX&apos;  # 设置时区 Asia/Chongqing</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>在Terminal输入</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">python manages.py  # 可以查看后面带的参数</span><br><span class=\"line\">python manage.py migrate # 会在在数据库中创建10张表</span><br><span class=\"line\">python manage.py createsuperuser # 创建超级管理员</span><br><span class=\"line\">python manage.py runserver # 运行django，在网址后面加admin,输入用户名和密码进入管理员界面</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n","prev":{"title":"通过命令创建Django项目(虚拟环境中)","slug":"pythonvirtualenv"},"next":{"title":"redis基础","slug":"redis的安装"},"link":"http://yoursite.com/post/django/"}